}}'''内淋巴'''（英文：Endolymph），是[[內耳|内耳]]中的一种液体，存在于[[膜迷路|膜迷路]]中<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|chapter=Anatomy, Head and Neck, Ear Endolymph|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK531505/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=30285400|first=Jarett|last=Casale|first2=Amit|last2=Agarwal|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2022-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220218103251/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK531505/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Endolymph - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/endolymph|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527151725/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/endolymph}}</ref>。内淋巴与[[外淋巴|外淋巴]]相对应，但不直接接触<ref name=":0" />。内淋巴中的主要[[阳离子|阳离子]]为[[鉀離子|钾离子]]，[[鈉離子|钠离子]]和钾离子的浓度分别为0.91[[體積莫耳濃度#单位|mM]]、154mM<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Observations on the electrochemistry of the cochlear endolymph of the rat: a quantitative study of its electrical potential and ionic composition as determined by means of flame spectrophotometry|url=https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/10.1098/rspb.1968.0066|last=Bosher|first=S. K.|last2=Warren|first2=R. L.|date=1968-11-05|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society of London. Series B. Biological Sciences|issue=1023|doi=10.1098/rspb.1968.0066|volume=171|pages=227–247|last3=Hallpike|first3=Charles Skinner|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2019-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024153518/https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/10.1098/rspb.1968.0066}}</ref>。内淋巴液又称“斯卡帕液（Scarpa's fluid）”，以纪念[[意大利|意大利]]解剖学家[[安东尼奥·斯卡帕|安东尼奥·斯卡帕]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Antonio Scarpa (1752–1832)|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3566389/|last=Grzybowski|first=Andrzej|last2=Sak|first2=Jarosław|date=2013|journal=Journal of Neurology|issue=2|doi=10.1007/s00415-012-6658-4|volume=260|pages=695–696|issn=0340-5354|pmc=3566389|pmid=22926229|access-date=2021-03-12|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111162043/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3566389/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Endolymph|url=https://www.imaios.com/en/e-Anatomy/Anatomical-Parts/Endolymph|accessdate=2021-03-12|work=IMAIOS|language=en}}</ref>。

== 结构 ==
内耳的核心部分为[[骨迷路|骨迷路]]，由[[耳蜗|耳蜗]]和[[前庭系统|前庭系统]]组成。骨迷路内有[[膜迷路|膜迷路]]，膜迷路中含有内淋巴；而[[外淋巴|外淋巴]]包裹膜迷路，介于骨迷路与膜迷路之间，起保护作用<ref>{{Cite web|title=Membranous Labyrinth - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/membranous-labyrinth|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Membranous labyrinth {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/membranous-labyrinth?lang=us|accessdate=2021-03-11|last=Hacking|first=Craig|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429054558/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/membranous-labyrinth?lang=us}}</ref>。

== 成分及功能 ==
外淋巴和内淋巴液中特有的离子成分可调节听觉[[毛细胞|毛细胞]]的电化学冲动。内淋巴液比周围的液体[[電勢|电势]]要高，其中比外淋巴液的电势高出80-90[[毫伏|毫伏]]，这是因为内淋巴液含有更高浓度的钾离子而外淋巴液含有更高浓度的钠离子，这被称为{{link-en|耳蜗内电位|Endocochlear potential}}<ref name=":12">{{Cite web|title=Endolymph and Perilymph - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/endolymph-and-perilymph|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Ion transport in guinea pig cochlea. I. Potassium and sodium transport|journal=[[Acta_Otolaryngol|Acta Otolaryngol]]|issue=1–2|doi=10.3109/00016487809124717|year=1978|volume=86|pages=22–34|pmid=696294|vauthors=Konishi T, Hamrick PE, Walsh PJ}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Supporting sensory transduction: cochlear fluid homeostasis and the endocochlear potential|last=Wangemann|first=Philine|date=2006-10-01|journal=The Journal of Physiology|issue=Pt 1|doi=10.1113/jphysiol.2006.112888|volume=576|pages=11–21|issn=0022-3751|pmc=1995626|pmid=16857713}}</ref>。

内淋巴高浓度的钾离子由{{link-en|耳蜗血管纹|Stria vascularis of cochlear duct}}分泌，可以形成毛细胞中的去极化电流，这被称为“机电转导（mechano-electric transduction）”电流<ref name=":0" />。内淋巴中的高电势使得钾离子可以在“毛束”机械刺激过程中进入毛细胞中<ref name=":0" />。

* '''[[听觉|听觉]]'''：在耳蜗管道中的内淋巴的波动，可刺激听觉[[感受器|感受器]]，后者将此振动转化为神经冲动（通过[[耳蜗神经|耳蜗神经]]）传向[[大脑|大脑]]。
* '''[[平衡觉|平衡觉]]'''：在[[半规管|半规管]]管道中的内淋巴的转动变速，可刺激平衡觉感受器，后者可将此信号（通过[[前庭神经|前庭神经]]）传向大脑。

== 临床 ==
对内淋巴液的不规则扰动可导致[[晕动病|晕动病]]，譬如持续转圈或在崎岖路上行车<ref>{{Cite web|title=How does the dizzying motion after-effect (from spinning on a swing) affect hand-eye coordination?|url=http://scienceline.ucsb.edu/getkey.php?key=3477|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=|publisher=UCSB|archive-date=2020-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923134828/http://scienceline.ucsb.edu/getkey.php?key=3477}}</ref>。

此外，有研究认为[[梅尼埃病|梅尼埃病]]是内耳的内淋巴、外淋巴单向流动受阻造成<ref name=":12" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Histopathology of Meniere’s disease|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5344024/|last=Cureoglu|first=Sebahattin|last2=da Costa Monsanto|first2=Rafael|date=2016-12|journal=Operative techniques in otolaryngology--head and neck surgery|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.otot.2016.10.003|volume=27|pages=194–204|issn=1043-1810|pmc=5344024|pmid=28286401|last3=Paparella|first3=Michael M.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Meniere's disease - Symptoms and causes|url=https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/menieres-disease/symptoms-causes/syc-20374910|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=Mayo Clinic|language=en|archive-date=2013-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530232848/http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/menieres-disease/DS00535/DSECTION=symptoms}}</ref>。

